Package: hospEpi
Type: Package
Title: Perform Basic Hospital Epidemiology Tasks
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Nate Peters <npeters1322@gmail.com>
Maintainer: Nate Peters <npeters1322@gmail.com>
Description: This package assists with performing different epidemiological tasks in a hospital setting,
  like providing statistics related to diseases and exposures (ex. odds ratio) and networks of patient
  movements.
